metadata.description:
My forever profile picture.

One of the first AI creation I did and indeed one of my most-loved one, over 2000 thousand trials I never managed to do anything close to this one and I think this number will just increase more and more.

I don't want to express peace in my art, but violence and all the things that make our primate mind react in unpredictable way.


Made with the original CLIP GUIDED DIFFUSION in September 2021.
